330
00:15:09,159 --> 00:15:09,679
Let's go.

331
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:41,760
President Gu,

332
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:42,400
your tea.

333
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:48,119
Your hand.

334
00:15:49,200 --> 00:15:50,440
Director Feng sure has a lot of free time.

335
00:15:50,919 --> 00:15:51,599
Every day,

336
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:53,159
