338
00:15:55,840 --> 00:15:56,520
I'm warning you.

339
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,080
From now on, not just with Feng Ziang,

340
00:15:58,760 --> 00:15:59,479
but within the company,

341
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,640
you are not allowed to have

342
00:16:01,640 --> 00:16:02,960
