343
00:16:03,359 --> 00:16:03,960
I understand.

344
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:05,440
From now on in the company,

345
00:16:05,599 --> 00:16:06,239
I will be careful.

346
00:16:06,880 --> 00:16:08,039
I hope you really pay attention.

347
00:16:10,039 --> 00:16:10,960
I want to advance a

348
00:16:11,320 --> 00:16:12,119
Chinese company's

349
00:16:12,119 --> 00:16:13,559
