407
00:17:38,760 --> 00:17:40,040
Do you think I'm really that naive?

408
00:17:40,599 --> 00:17:41,160
What do you mean?

409
00:17:41,439 --> 00:17:42,160
You're bluffing.

410
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,079
Bluffing who?

411
00:17:43,800 --> 00:17:44,439
Everyone.

412
00:17:45,199 --> 00:17:46,119
Didn't you fall for it too?

413
00:17:48,599 --> 00:17:50,199
Up ahead is Feimanchi's sales floor.

414
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:52,319
Pretty efficient.

415
00:17:52,599 --> 00:17:53,760
Getting straight to the point upon arrival.

416
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:54,520
Let's go.

417
00:17:54,920 --> 00:17:55,439
Wait a moment.

418
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:57,319
Excuse me.

419
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:58,160
I'd like to ask,

420
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,079
