427
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:09,520
All right.

428
00:18:09,800 --> 00:18:10,479
We are from

429
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:11,439
Flair.

430
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,160
You're from Flair?

431
00:18:13,520 --> 00:18:14,680
We will replace Feimanchi

432
00:18:14,880 --> 00:18:15,599
and become the next

433
00:18:15,599 --> 00:18:16,520
