434
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,160
We are currently in the discussion phase.

435
00:18:18,439 --> 00:18:19,359
We're here today to see the site.

436
00:18:20,520 --> 00:18:21,199
We've already wasted

437
00:18:21,199 --> 00:18:22,199
