438
00:18:22,439 --> 00:18:22,839
Let's go.

439
00:18:22,839 --> 00:18:23,439
I'm sorry.

440
00:18:25,719 --> 00:18:26,560
This visit

441
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:27,520
